| 2. Title bar 80px hard-coded | 🔴 **LEGIT** | Hard-coded padding wastes space on non-macOS |
| 3. CodeMirror dark: true | ✅ FIXED | Parameter is dynamic, not hard-coded |
| 4. Preview left-aligned | ✅ FIXED | Centered with `justify-content: center` |
| 5. Theme switcher overflow | ✅ FIXED | Full viewport clamping implemented |
| 6. AI model picker overflow | ✅ FIXED | Full viewport clamping implemented |

**Result:** **5 of 6 issues are resolved or non-existent.** Only the title bar 80px padding is a genuine design issue worth addressing.

