| Issue | Verdict | Notes |
|-------|---------|-------|
| 7. AI Chat padding wobble | ✓ ALREADY FIXED | Input uses `margin: 0`, body uses consistent 16px padding |
| 8. File Explorer padding mismatch | ✗ LEGIT | Search: 16px padding vs Panel header override: 12px right padding |
