| 11. Status bar path fixed width | ✗ LEGIT (modified) | Uses `50vw` (not 400px as reported), still potentially too restrictive |
| 12. Context menu font-weight 450 | ✓ NOT AN ISSUE | Uses `font-weight: 500`, not 450 |
| 13. Preview heading sizes | ✓ ALREADY FIXED | h4-h6 sized at 15.5px, distinct from body text |
| 14. Chevron rotation redundancy | ✗ LEGIT | Two separate systems: `.file-node-chevron.expanded` and `.chevron.open` |

