### **13. Preview heading sizes (Low)**
**Status: ALREADY FIXED ✓**

**Code:**
```css
/* typography.css - Preview headings */
.preview-content h1 { font-size: 28px; }    /* Line 18 */
.preview-content h2 { font-size: 22px; }    /* Line 27 */
.preview-content h3 { font-size: 18px; }    /* Line 36 */

